# cmake-toolset

See `AGENTS.md` for the full project rules.

## Key Rules

- Use `ports/Configure.cmake`, `test/CMakeLists.txt`,
  workflow files, and the upstream target tag as the
  main truth sources.
- Standard ports follow the usual template; treat
  `ssl/port.cmake`, `grpc/import.cmake`, and
  `protobuf/protobuf.cmake` as special cases.
- Patch matching is exact first, then same-minor
  fallback to the highest version `<=` target.
- `crosscompiling-host/` means host-side validation.
- Historical dependency chains are hints only.

## Workflow

See `.github/skills/port-upgrade/` or
`.agents/skills/port-upgrade/` for the upgrade
workflow.
